Welcome to Market Motive's SEO Practitioner Certification program. The goal of this learning program is to educate and train users wishing to develop an expertise in the Internet marketing discipline of Search Engine Optimization. The curriculum includes the following sections, covering the following areas of Search Engine Optimization

Section 1: Introduction to SEO
Section 2: On-Page Best Practices
Section 3: Keyword Research
Section 4: Competitive Analysis
Section 5: Design & Architecture
Section 6: Site Optimization & Best Practices
Section 7: Link-Building
Section 8: SEO for Local Search
Section 9: SEO Site Audits
Section 10: SEO Algorithm Updates
Section 11: SEO Tracking
Supplemental Material: SEO Career Path
Supplemental Material: SEO Tools
